Package compiler.postfix

Class Token

java.lang.Object
compiler.postfix.Token
public class Token extends Object
Wrapper for different tokens (strings) that can appear in infix and postfix expressions. Tokens are constructed with the of(String) method to allow reuse of frequently used Tokens, which are also public members of this class.
Author:
Alex Mandelias
